ygData.messageBody:
Personally I've all but given up on playing my DeSK... I got to level 35,
found it a major struggle to get anywhere, and then all my friends who I'd
somehow managed to keep up with, managed to get into and out of 40...

I still love the SK, but it's just too much of an uphill battle right now.

Hmm, might start a new one on TZ or VZ...

H
